AWS Customers

Any AWS customer who wants to improve their operational efficiency at scale.
Automation reduces errors associated with manual intervention, and can reduce time to resolution of common issues should use automation.

Architects

Infrastructure experts responsible for resource design and deployment who want to automate their environment's deployment and configuration tasks should use automation.
These are architects trusted to build automation solutions.

Administrators

Administrators who want to reliably resolve common issues, improve troubleshooting efficiency, and reduce repetitive operations should use automation.

Users

Users who want to save time and use repeatable processes to automate time-consuming tasks that they typically perform manually should use automation.